            <h2>Theme Parks</h2>
            <h3><strong>Riding the VR and AR at Theme Parks</strong></h3>
            <div class="container">
                <img src="assets/images/disneyland.png" alt="title" width="300px">
            </div>
            <div class="container">
                <img src="assets/images/universal.png" alt="title" width="300px">
            </div>
            <h4>Walt Disney has announced their intention to build a theme park in the metaverse in the next few years, and we already have amusement park rides that are enhanced by AR and VR.
            </h4>
            <h4>Universal Studios Hollywood will also import a Mario Kart-themed ride from Japan that uses augmented reality to create the illusion that the user is interacting with virtual characters and objects. Visor-like glasses will enable theme park guests to engage with digital creations on the ride in real-time.
            </h4>
        </div>
    </div>



